  <brief_title>Use of the SNAP II Electroencephalography (EEG) Monitor in Outpatients Undergoing Surgery/Procedures With Sedation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of the SNAP II EEG Monitor in Outpatients Undergoing Surgery/Procedures With Sedation</official_title>
