  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if the SNAP II electroencephalography (EEG) monitor
      accurately reflects changes in sedation level in outpatients undergoing surgery or procedures
      with sedation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
